nodejs linux - ubuntu instalation

1.download a tar file on: https://nodejs.org/en/download
2.in download folder: tar -xf node-v20.11.1-linux-x64.tar.xz
3.got to bin: node-v20.11.1-linux-x64.tar.xz cd bin/
4. move nodejs folder to ~/
5. make globall acess: sudo nano .bashrc
6. write: "export PATH=$PATH:/home/lb/nodejs/bin"

nestjs linux - ubuntu instalation
7. Nest CLI instalation: npm i -g @nestjs/cli
8. yarm npm instalation: npm install --global yarn
9. nest new project-name

# update npm
Run npm install -g npm@10.4.0 to update!
